comments.message:
if you use type = 'combo', it will check for you:

$ meson setup testbuild -Dfru-device-16bitdetectmode=MODE_3

 meson.build:1:0: ERROR: Value "MODE_3" (of type "string") for combo option "Different modes to detect 16-bit address EEPROM devices. MODE_1 is current and default mode." is not one of the choices. Possible choices are (as string): "MODE_1", "MODE_2".
